
linux_utils

running a process in background
```
watch top &
```

list your background jobs with

```
jobs
```

bring to foreground
```
fg 1
```

kill it with "`Ctrl-C`"


Install SMB-shared printer
```
sudo apt install python3-smbc
sudo apt install smbclient
testparm -v
sudo touch /etc/samba/smb.conf 
```
